      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1031</offset>
        <text>At the global scale, nitrification accounts for about half of the nitrate consumed by growing phytoplankton.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1140</offset>
        <text>A consequence is that many previous attempts to quantify marine carbon export, particularly those based on inappropriate use of the f-ratio (a measure of the efficiency of the 'biological pump'), are significant overestimates.
</text>
      </sentence>
